{"tid":2266411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒：日本政府擬將宙斯盾艦大型化","createTime":"2020-11-01T09:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T10:11:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3e95c9700ef04263e29ec1832cca8d88c5af1d","tid":2266411,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stream.881903.com/public/966a5f6ec1a3b947695cd8cbfe8adac9/2020/11/b87f417e3665a256f88c7b76bf7a9614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstream.881903.com%2Fpublic%2F966a5f6ec1a3b947695cd8cbfe8adac9%2F2020%2F11%2Fb87f417e3665a256f88c7b76bf7a9614.jpg&h=6c828ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本共同社引述官方消息人士說，日本政府撤銷陸基宙斯盾反導計劃後，正研究將裝備宙斯盾火控系統的軍艦大型化，防衛省委托的民間企業最快月中提交中期報告，當局將在年底敲定大方向。 消息人士說，防衛省計劃在新建的軍艦，裝備美製&ldquo;SPY-7&rdquo;相控陣雷達，比日本現役宙斯盾艦配備的&ldquo;SPY-1D&rdquo;更高，為保持艦體平衡，必須擴大船的寬度，日本3月服役的摩耶號宙斯盾艦，標準排水量8200噸，新軍艦若擴寬數米，預計排水量增將至約9000噸，成為日本最大的軍艦。      日本 宙斯盾艦<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2364218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2364218&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh5IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=02c07c0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2364218</a>"},{"pid":"56496e5056e06d4a31168af103be0ded1a5a3fb9","tid":2266411,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T10:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}